                              <input type="radio" asp-for="Difficulty" value="&exercises=All&page=1&All=0&Bands=0&Bench=0&Dumbbell=0&EZBar=0&Kettlebell=0&MachineStrength=0&MachineCardio=0&Barbell=0&BodyOnly=0&ExerciseBall=0&FoamRoll=0&PullBar=0&WeightPlate=0&Other=0&Strength=0&Stretching=0&Powerlifting=0&OlympicWeightLifting=0&Beginner=1&Intermediate=0&Expert=0"/>Beginner
